node.text: Guys thanks for sticking around things here seem to be normalizing on the platform after I experienced a pretty serious dip and likes and interactions for quite some time. A lot of you guys reached out to me and mentioned it that seems to be going well again for the time being and I just wanted to thank you guys for staying with us. Hope you have a great weekend.

node.text: Guys, given what I’m seeing given what I’m hearing from other conservative accounts given the full frontal attack by big tech on anyone who is a conservative this is where you need to go to stay in touch with me. Go to my website, click the link in my bio, and just send me your email that way whatever happens I have a way to let you know where I actually end up. It’s simple, it takes two seconds, you do t have to buy anything, but it will allow me a place to make sure that I can still get my incredible followers the Content that they’ve come here for in the ever increasingly likely event that I’m thrown off and totally deplatformed.

node.text: If you’re from Georgia you have three hours to get in line and vote to save your country. Don’t squander that opportunity!
